19hours from first petition to fully resolved (most of which i was not logged on) is pretty great CS by sony imo. My advice, /report the text as soon as you know something is wrong, /petition (and use /viewpetition to make sure it stays up), and email your GM through the Everquest site. It worked for me at least.  Also, please be aware of it and don't let yourself get fooled. Good luck all!<br>
<br>
Weee I'm happy<br>
<br>
*heads over to the kudos page*<br>
<br>
Maeluuin<br>
